                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.—Received October 1, 1900.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pekin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-09-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 29, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger reports that the Russian legation has to-day been removed to
                    Tientsin.)</p>
